<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Let’s Car’raoke | San Diego Karaoke Ride Experiences</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Let’s Car’raoke turns transportation into the highlight of the outing with private karaoke rides, premium private transportation, and care-forward assisted rides in San Diego."
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container header-inner">
        <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Home">
          <img
            src="/assets/lets-carraoke.png"
            alt="Let’s Car’raoke logo"
            loading="eager"
            width="200"
            height="100"
          />
        </a>

        <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Primary">
          <a class="nav-link" href="/services">Services</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="page">
      <h1>Turn travel time into the highlight of the outing.</h1>

      <p>
        Let’s Car’raoke is an entertainment-forward private ride experience in San Diego — hosted karaoke rides,
        premium private transportation, and care-forward assisted rides designed around the moment.
      </p>

      <p class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn" href="/services">Explore services</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/pricing">View pricing</a>
      </p>

      <section class="cards" aria-label="Featured services">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Signature Car’raoke (60 min)</h2>
          <p>Your private karaoke ride — hosted, high-energy, unforgettable.</p>
          <p><a class="text-link" href="/services/signature-carraoke-60">Learn more</a></p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h2>Premium Private Car’raoke (90 min)</h2>
          <p>More time. More songs. More celebration.</p>
          <p><a class="text-link" href="/services/premium-private-carraoke-90">Learn more</a></p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h2>Luxury / VIP Car’raoke</h2>
          <p>Elevated presentation for VIP guests and premium occasions.</p>
          <p><a class="text-link" href="/services/luxury-vip-carraoke">Learn more</a></p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section id="contact" class="contact" aria-label="Contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Call or text:
          <a class="text-link" href="tel:+18586487464">(858) 648-SING (7464)</a>
          <br />
          Website:
          <a class="text-link" href="https://www.letscarraoke.net">www.letscarraoke.net</a>
        </p>

        <p>
          Ready to book? Start with <a class="text-link" href="/pricing">Pricing</a> or browse
          <a class="text-link" href="/services">Services</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <style>
      .page {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
      }

      .header-inner {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .main-nav {
        margin-left: auto;
      }

      .nav-link {
        color: #000;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-right: 12px;
      }

      .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #111;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
      }

      .card {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1rem;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .text-link {
        color: #000;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .contact {
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>

